        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Pell Grant Sustainability Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Education to calculate the maximum award amount for Pell Grants for award year 2022-2023 and each subsequent award year by indexing the award amount to the rate of inflation.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
